title: Travel Sisters: Female Travel App

creator: zwodnik
descriptionHtml:
Travel Sisters is a social travel app connecting women who love to chat, meet up and travel together.

Host as sister: find a free accommodation with a local sister as part of a cultural exchange. It's an awesome opportunity to get to know locals and see how they live.

Travel sister: traveling together is always safer and cheaper. Find a female travel buddy who is looking at the same type of adventure as you. Sharing moments with someone else is half of the experience.

Meet up: when visiting a city for the first time a great way to start your trip is to meet up with a local sister for a coffee or to show you around. Usually the places locals go are completely different and many times better! Discover new places and make new friends.

Chat: dreaming of your next trip is exciting, but planning the perfect trip takes time and knowledge. Offer your help and share your experience with other sisters to inspire and guide them.

Female only: Travel Sisters welcomes all females age 18 or older. We use photo verification to increase female safety and avoid fake profiles.

Free: It's totally free. You can chat with as many sisters as you like.
descriptionShort: Female only social travel app empowering women to travel together.

descriptionHtml:
Travel Ladies connect women who love to travel. Whether you're a solo traveler or you travel with others we help you to make travel friends and always travel together.

Find a travel buddy: traveling together is always safer and cheaper. Find a female travel companion who is looking at the same type of adventure as you. Sharing moments with someone else is half of the experience.

Meet nearby travelers and locals: when visiting a city for the first time a great way to start your trip is to meet up with a local lady for a coffee or to show you around. Usually the places locals go are completely different and many times better! Discover new places and make new friends.

Find a free accommodation: local ladies offer a free accommodation as part of a cultural exchange. It's an awesome opportunity to get to know locals and see how they live though our female only couch-surfing platform.

Seek travel advice get the best travel advice from our female travelers who know how to travel the world as a woman and stay safe! Share your upcoming trip or planned itinerary to get the best travel advice and recommendation.

Chat and share your experience: dreaming of your next trip is exciting, but planning the perfect trip takes time and knowledge. Offer your help and share your experience with other ladies to inspire and guide them.

Female only: Travel Ladies welcomes all females age 18 or older. We use photo verification to increase female safety and avoid fake profiles.

Free: It's totally free. You can connect with as many ladies as you like.


Why is Travel Ladies the best solo travel app?

You are not alone

As a solo traveler there are many times when you are alone and feel a little lonely, but you are never alone. This is an opportunity to meet nearby female travelers who are looking for conversation, connection, support and fun. Open the app, set your travel status and meet.

Stay safe when couch-surfing

No doubt your main concern as a solo traveler is safety. Popular couch-surfing platforms are full of male predators looking for vulnerable women. That's why we offer a female only couch-surfing platform where you can meet and stay with local females all over the world.

Easy travel planning

Planning your trip as a solo traveler can often bring on many fears. There are a lot of things that can go wrong when traveling on your own. If you want information about a place you are going to just ask for advice. Female travelers who have been there can provide the most valuable and unique insights.
descriptionShort: Female only travel app empowering women to travel and explore the world.

descriptionHtml:
Travel Ladies is a female only travel app connecting women who love to travel and meet new people.

Meet new people

Find travel buddies

Traveling together is always safer and cheaper. Find female travel buddies who are looking at the same type of adventure as you. Sharing moments with someone else is half of the experience.

Meet locals

When visiting a city for the first time a great way to start your trip is to meet up with a local woman for a coffee or to show you around. Usually the places locals go are completely different and many times better! Discover new places and make new friends.

Stay with locals

Couch surfing is a great way of cultural exchange and an awesome opportunity to get to know local women and see how they live, learn about their culture and discover the secret places every city hides. Find a couch to sleep on and make unforgettable encounters!

Share your travel stories

Have you recently traveled somewhere and wanted to share your travel stories with others? Be it a memorable view of the city and surrounding areas, an outdoor experience, a natural wonder or a delicious local meal. Start sharing your stories to inspire and empower women around the world.

Chat

Chat with women from all over the world. Talk about your past trips, greatest travel moments, favorite destinations and future adventures.

Female only

Travel Ladies welcomes all females age 18 or older. We use photo verification to increase safety and avoid fake profiles.

Free

It's totally free. You can connect with as many women as you like.



As a female traveler, you can:

* connect with women around the world who share the passion for traveling
* share your travel stories
* see the locals in the selected area
* hang out with nearby travelers and locals
* find local hosts offering a couch to sleep on
* share your next trip to connect with locals and travelers heading in the same direction

As a local women, you can

* meet up with travelers visiting your city for a coffee or a drink
* host travelers coming to your hometown and offer a free couch to sleep on
* spend some time with travelers and show them around
* give a ride to the places they need to go
* give advice about amazing places to see around the city
* offer a language exchange to anyone who is interested in learning or improving local language

Travel Ladies is a female-only travel app connecting women who love to solo travel and meet new people. It is a great place to meet local women around the world, find travel buddies, couch surf with female hosts, share travel memories and find travel tips for every area of travel.

Meet local women

Travel Ladies makes it easy to connect with local women who share the passion for traveling and want to share their experiences with other women. You will learn more about the culture, sights, and hidden gems of your destination from talking to real women than you ever will from a guidebook or even the internet.

Find travel buddies

Traveling together is always safer and cheaper. Find female travel buddies who are looking at the same type of adventure as you. Be it backpacking all over Europe, hiking in the mountains or just day walking in the UK. Don't miss the opportunity to find exactly the right travel buddy for you.

Share your travel memories

Have you recently traveled somewhere and wanted to share your travel memories with others? Be it a memorable view of the city and surrounding areas, an outdoor experience, a natural wonder or a delicious local meal. Start sharing your memories to inspire and empower solo female travelers around the world.

Couch surf with female hosts

Couch surfing is a great way of cultural exchange and an awesome opportunity to get to know local women and see how they live, learn about their culture and discover the secret places every city hides. Find a couch to sleep on and make unforgettable encounters!

Discover great places to visit

Are you looking for interesting cities with historical influence? Fantastic cuisine? Breathtaking mountains? Beautiful islands and beaches? Is safety your number one priority? Our community of solo female travelers shares travel tips from locals who live there and memories from female travelers who have visited those places.

Find language partners

Find conversation partners and improve your speaking with language exchange.

Why should you use Travel Ladies as a solo female traveler?

* to meet locals and make new friends
* to connect with women around the world who share the passion for traveling
* to share your travel memories and inspire other women to travel the world too!
* to find local hosts offering a couch to sleep on
* to connect with travelers heading in the same direction
* to practice a language with native speakers

Why should you use Travel Ladies as a local woman?

* to meet up with travelers visiting your city for a coffee or a drink
* to host travelers coming to your hometown and offer a free couch to sleep on
* to spend some time with travelers and show them around
* to give advice about amazing places to see around the city
* to offer a language exchange to anyone who is interested in learning your local language

If you want to follow updates on Travel Ladies:

- Website: https://travelladies.app/
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/female_couch_surfing/
- TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@female_couch_surfing
descriptionShort: Meet, Stay and Travel with Women Around the World

Find travel buddies

Share your travel memories

Travel Ladies is a female-only travel app connecting women who love to travel solo and meet new people.

Meet local women

Travel Ladies makes it easy to connect with local women who share the passion for traveling and want to share their experiences with other women. You will learn more about the culture, sights, safety and hidden gems of your destination from talking to real women than you ever will from a guidebook or even the internet.

Find travel buddies

Traveling together is always safer and cheaper. Find female travel buddies who are looking at the same type of adventure as you. Be it backpacking all over Europe, hiking in the mountains or just day walking in the UK. Don't miss the opportunity to find exactly the right travel buddy for you.

Share your travel memories

Have you recently traveled somewhere and wanted to share your travel memories with others? Be it a memorable view of the city and surrounding areas, an outdoor experience, a natural wonder or a delicious local meal. Start sharing your memories to inspire and empower solo female travelers and backpackers around the world.

Couch surf with female hosts

Couch surfing is a great way of cultural exchange and an awesome opportunity to get to know local women and see how they live, learn about their culture and discover the secret places every city hides. Find a couch to sleep on and make unforgettable encounters!

Discover great places to visit

Are you looking for interesting cities with historical influence? Fantastic cuisine? Breathtaking mountains? Beautiful islands and beaches? Is safety your number one priority? Our community of solo female travelers shares travel tips from locals who live there and memories from female travelers who have visited those places.

Discuss

Ask questions, get advice and share travel stories with women around the world. We have travel groups for solo travel, backpacking, hiking, traveling on a budget, van life, digital nomads and more.

Why should you use Travel Ladies as a solo female traveler or backpacker?

* to meet locals and make new friends
* to connect with women around the world who share the passion for traveling
* to share your travel memories and inspire other women to travel the world too!
* to find local hosts offering a couch to sleep on
* to connect with travelers heading in the same direction

Why should you use Travel Ladies as a local woman?

* to meet up with travelers visiting your city for a coffee or a drink
* to host travelers coming to your hometown and offer a free couch to sleep on
* to spend some time with travelers and show them around
* to give advice about amazing places to see around the city
* to offer a language exchange to anyone who is interested in learning your local language

If you want to follow updates on Travel Ladies:

- Website: https://travelladies.app/
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/travelladies.app/
- TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@travelladies.app
- Pinterest: https://www.pinterest.co.uk/travelladiesapp/
- Github: https://github.com/TravelLadies
descriptionShort: Connecting adventure women who love to travel solo and meet new people

appDetails.developerName: Travel Ladies

title:
Travel Ladies
1.17.155

creator: Travel Ladies
descriptionHtml:
Travel Ladies is a travel app designed specifically for women to meet new people, find travel buddies, and stay with local women across the globe—for free.

Meet New People

Travel Ladies makes it easy to connect with local women who share a passion for traveling and are eager to share their experiences. By talking with real women, you'll gain insights into the culture, sights, safety, and hidden gems of your destination—far beyond what any guidebook or online resource can offer.

Find Travel Buddies

Traveling together is not only safer but also more affordable. Whether you're backpacking across Europe, hiking in the mountains, or just enjoying a day walk in the UK, you can find travel buddies who match your adventure style. Don’t miss out on finding the perfect travel companion for your journey.

Stay with Locals

Experience cultural exchange through hospitality exchange. It’s an incredible opportunity to connect with local women, see how they live, learn about their culture, and discover the hidden gems of every city. Find a place to stay and make unforgettable memories!

Share Your Travel Memories

Have you recently explored a new destination and want to share your experiences? Whether it’s a breathtaking view, an outdoor adventure, a natural wonder, or a delicious local meal, start sharing your memories to inspire and empower solo female travelers and backpackers worldwide.

Discover Great Places to Visit

Looking for cities rich in history, fantastic cuisine, breathtaking mountains, or beautiful beaches? Is safety your top priority? Our community of solo female travelers shares valuable tips from locals and fellow travelers who have explored these destinations.

Discuss and Connect

Ask questions, seek advice, and share your travel stories with women from around the world. Join our travel groups focused on solo travel, backpacking, hiking, budget travel, van life, digital nomads, and more.

Stay Connected

Follow us for updates and inspiration:

- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/travelladies.app
- TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@travelladies.app

creator: Travel Ladies
descriptionHtml:
Travel Ladies is a travel app designed exclusively for women to explore the world confidently, meet fellow female travelers, and immerse in authentic local experiences. Whether you're looking to find travel buddies, connect with local women for stays, or share travel stories, Travel Ladies creates a supportive and empowering community for women on the move.

Meet New People

With Travel Ladies, expanding your global network is easier than ever. The app lets you connect with women travelers from various backgrounds, cultures, and countries, fostering meaningful friendships. Whether you're looking for someone to grab coffee with or a fellow traveler to explore a new city, Travel Ladies brings women together wherever their journey takes them.

Find Travel Buddies

Planning a trip but don’t want to travel alone? Travel Ladies helps you find the perfect travel buddy. Whether you want someone to explore a new city, hike a trail, or enjoy a beach vacation with, the app matches you with travelers who have similar interests, destinations, and schedules. Travel is better together!

Stay with Local Women Through Hospitality Exchange

Experience the warmth of local hospitality through Travel Ladies' unique exchange system. The app enables you to connect with local women who are offering a safe place to stay, making your trip more authentic and budget-friendly. It's a great way to immerse yourself in the local culture while building friendships with hosts who understand your journey.

Share Travel Memories and Engage in Travel Discussions

Document your travel adventures and share them with the Travel Ladies community! Post photos, write about your experiences, and engage in discussions with other members. From travel tips to destination guides, the app is a hub for exchanging stories, advice, and memories that inspire future trips.
